data.description: Beautifully renovated tri-level home on a fenced 1-acre lot in Pueblo West. Well designed 4BR, 3BA, tri-level home with 1979 SF. U-shaped gravel driveway for dual street access. Gorgeous LVP floors, modern light fixtures, & lighted ceiling fans throughout. Central air & heat for year round comfort. Open floor plan w/ spacious living areas for privacy & comfort. The vaulted Living Rm has a view window to the front yard. It flows  into the Dining Area & Kitchen making it a great area for entertaining. The Dining Area has a slider to the backyard patio for outdoor dining options. The Kitchen features a counter bar & white cabinets w/ butcher block countertops. Appl incl a smooth top range oven, built-in microwave, dishwasher, & side by side refrigerator. The UL hosts 3BRs & 2BAs. The Primary Owner's Suite is a private retreat w/ slider to a 10x10 deck w/ stairs to the backyard patio. There is a walk in closet & an adjoining 5pc Bathroom w/ tile floor that incl a new vanity, mirror, jetted tub & separate shower. 2 more UL BRs share a Full Hall Bathroom w/ new vanity, mirror, & tub/shower. The LL offers a Family Rm w/ gas log fireplace, a Laundry Rm w/ washer & dryer that stays, & a BR & Shower Bathroom, that offers a private space for guests or in-laws. The 2-car garage has a newer epoxy floor, storage, & door opener. The fully fenced, level backyard has an expanded side yard for RV or small boat storage.  Located within 5 miles of schools & parks. Easy drive to Pueblo Reservoir.
